text.headline: Larchmont Neighborhood
text.text: Madelyn and Meira snuggle on the sofa shortly after waking up this morning on July 12, 2014 in Norfolk, Virginia. After a quick breakfast and some last-minute packing, I was dropped off at the train station. I am currently en route to NYC and will be missing these two for the next few days. #norfolk #virginia #va #family #daughters #sisters #snuggle #love #loveinthefirstperson #leavingsucks #thesevencities #america #usa

text.headline: The Half King
text.text: Spent this morning installing "The Invisible Yoke" exhibition at The Half King in NYC with @jamesbprice and @annavanlenten. The show opens with an artist talk @ 7:30PM on Tuesday, July 15. Come out, have some dinner/drinks and toss good questions or rotten vegetables at me. #newyork #nyc #exhibition #installation #theinvisibleyoke #thehalfking #theamericancondition
